-- Switzerland's ABB Wins $89 Million Order to Power Saudi Financial District
-- Antonio Ligi
-- 2010-06-30T08:05:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/switzerland-s-abb-wins-89-million-order-to-power-saudi-financial-district.html

          
          
             ABB Ltd. won an order worth $89
million from the Saudi Electricity Company to build a new
substation to ensure reliable power supplies for the King
Abdullah Financial District in the city of Riyadh.  
 The Swiss company commented in an e-mailed statement.  
          
          


  


        